releases.name: Test
releases.body:
You must create the following directory as creation is handled by the updater not included in this test release:

```
%appdata%\BetterDiscord\lib
```

Ignore any missing features such as the uninstaller and advanced settings

releases.name: v0.2.8
releases.body:
Tons of error catching.
Themes must be named *.theme.css
Plugins must be named *.plugin.js
Added error handling, fallbacks for emotedata and a log file output.
Required for Discord 0.0.285

releases.name: v0.1.5 beta with MacOS Support
releases.body:
# v0.1.5 beta
- Required for js1.3

# Changelog
- MacOS Support by [Candunc](https://github.com/Candunc)
- New and improved resource loading
- Emotedata caching (expires daily)
- Public servers (list from reddit: https://redd.it/3iepbt)
- Voice chat mode http://puu.sh/kWU1t.png
- BetterTTV emotes
- Twitchemotes.com api for twitch emotes https://twitchemotes.com/apidocs
- BetterTTV api for BetterTTV emotes https://api.betterttv.net/emotes
